default’ (Clark, Dolman and Hoyt, 2010) and also work undertaken by WWF in ‘Protecting harbour porpoise in UK seas’ (Evans and Prior, 2012). It also builds upon 
defaultMarine Protected Areas for Whales, Dolphins and Porpoises: A world handbook for cetacean
default 
defaulthabitat conservation and planning 
default(Hoyt, 2011).
